item.title: Project 2: Modeling, Testing, and Predicting
item.description: Introduction For my project, I used the website: https://vincentarelbundock.github.io/Rdatasets/datasets.html as my source of finding my dataset for this project. The dataset that I am working with is called “Channing House Data”. This dataset contains data on the Channing Retirement House located in Fresno, California and stores collected data on men and women that passed through this house from 1964 until July 1, 1975. Their age on entry and also on leaving or death was recorded along with their sex.
